esource/Die_Warzau\"}, {\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999968610872353, \"rank\": 3.047091681046898e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.150243945706752e-46, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A gold medallist in men's singles earned 750 ATP points.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, that all stopped at the 2016 games in Rio.Evans is loving every moment of playing with Murray.And Judy, writing on X, was keen to remind fans of just how much the 34-year-old is giving up.Replying to a post that detailed Evans' sacrifice, the 64-year-old said: \\\"Most of you watching on Sunday and last night will not know this\\u2026\\u2026\\\"JUST IN:Emma Raducanu appears to take swipe at Judy Murray with 'astonishing' comment after new mixed doubles inviteA fan then said: \\\"You only have to see at Davis Cup & see that he thrives on these occasions & says so much about his character.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999124722580592, \"rank\": 8.753540360420231e-05, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\"}, {\"begin\": 1387, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Judy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For those saying it's a no brainer- you do understand how ranking affects earnings?\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why his next tournament is a Challenger - it's about personal values/ethics.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And Judy replied by saying 'exactly x', making clear her admiration.Evans revealed before Team GB's win over Belgiumthat he'd considered withdrawing from the games.JUST IN:Adam Peaty update provided by Team GB team-mate as Olympics dream hangs in the balanceAnd he was delighted after helping Murray prolong his Olympics dream in the 37-year-old's last tournament as a tennis player.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1843, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999968610872353, \"rank\": 3.047091681046898e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1925, \"end\": 1935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 1955, \"end\": 1962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999968610872353, \"rank\": 3.04709168104689