 \"text\": \"Judy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For those saying it's a no brainer- you do understand how ranking affects earnings?\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why his next tournament is a Challenger - it's about personal values/ethics.\\\"\", \"from\": 4747, \"to\": 4831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Judy replied by saying 'exactly x', making clear her admiration.\", \"from\": 4833, \"to\": 4901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Evans revealed before Team GB's win over Belgiumthat he'd considered withdrawing from the games.\", \"from\": 4903, \"to\": 4999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4927, \"end\": 4934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999968610872353, \"rank\": 3.047091681046898e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"JUST IN:Adam Peaty update provided by Team GB team-mate as Olympics dream hangs in the balance  And he was delighted after helping Murray prolong his Olympics dream in the 37-year-old's last tournament as a tennis player.\", \"from\": 5001, \"to\": 5222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5008, \"end\": 5010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"score\": 0.6326431979338414, \"rank\": 0.5806696762170858, \"text\": \"IN\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\"}, {\"begin\": 5011, \"end\": 5021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 5041, \"end\": 5048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999968610872353, \"rank\": 3.047091681046898e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 5134, \"end\": 5140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0829746418975306e-27, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What happened again was incredible,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 5224, \"to\": 5270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are getting really close to doing something pretty special.\", \"from\": 5272, \"to\": 5335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We played great tonight.\", \"from\": 5337, \"to\": 5362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People see that, see how good we have been in tight moments, and we are getting better and better.\", \"from\": 5363, \"to\": 5461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LATEST SPORTS NEWS:  Most of you watching on Sunday and last night will not know this\\u2026\\u2026 \\u2764\\ufe0f\\ud83c\\uddec\\ud83c\\udde7https://t.co/kTACSJSWcd  \\\"I thought we were unlucky not to win 7-6 in the second set.\", \"from\": 5463, \"to\": 5640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How that volley went in, I still do not know.\", \"from\": 5641, \"to\": 5686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think he wants to go home, does he?\", \"from\": 5688, \"to\": 5733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's amazing to play with.\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am over the moon that I came.\\\"\", \"from\": 5761, \"to\": 5793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Murray, the former world No 1 cried on the court in the aftermath of the victory.\", \"from\": 5795, \"to\": 5883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5806, \"end\": 5812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0829746418975306e-27, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Explaining his tears, he said: \\\"Obviously it's unbelievably emotional.\", \"from\": 5885, \"to\": 5955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dan Evans and Andy Murray are just three victories away from winning gold at the Olympics  PA  \\\"You are obviously unbelievably happy and then, I do not know why it happens, it's like happy tears.\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\": 6152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5961, \"end\": 5970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"score\": 0.9999669350445916, \"rank\": 3.306604835885042e-05, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\"}, {\"begin\": 5975, \"end\": 5986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.150243945706752e-46, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really emotional at the end of the match.\", \"from\": 6153, \"to\": 6200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously extremely happy, excited that we managed to get through and another amazing finish so it takes a lot out of you that sort of stuff.\", \"from\": 6202, \"to\": 6344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am glad we get a day off tomorrow.\\\"\", \"from\": 6346, \"to\": 6384, \"entities\": []}]}"